{"tid":1623309,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"希望大家提醒下自己 走向極端係好危險","createTime":"2019-10-04T19:43:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:50:34.000Z","uid":46763,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8bd067e14438ff03a0a12bba70d3120b8db76198","tid":1623309,"uid":46763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:43:54.000Z","msg":"首先<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好畀仇恨蒙蔽</span></span></strong><br />\n唔係叫你唔好打爆野 係唔好喪失理智<br />\n怕自己人畀情緒綁架到失控<br />\n<br />\n第二 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極端行為思想容易出軌</span></span><br />\n睇返南韓逆權運動 獨裁者用反共名義走向極端<br />\n一樣冇民主白色恐怖<br />\n而家要既係自由民主呢個結果 唔好畀仇中情緒控制<br />\n<br />\n第三 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非永遠唔會同勇武割席</span></span><br />\n但唔好任意消費和理非<br />\n做左既野 唔會怪責 和理非會善後<br />\n但要不斷做文宣又同國際溝通 唔係咁易<br />\n<br />\n其實好難冇報復心態 但唔好走得太極端<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">最後</span><br />\n天崎：你覺得用咩方法好 做 鼓勵你做<br />\n但保持理性思考過再做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">講錯左 唔岩聽就唔好推</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e70a096c96dd9fca7c88c241f5347f0cb3d384","tid":1623309,"uid":54162,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:45:28.000Z","msg":"的確，最重要係唔好傷及無辜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69f7653c664a283398715dde06fa50a0ec13651","tid":1623309,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:47:37.000Z","msg":"要不停反醒自己，先有進步"},{"pid":"c5ee02b6a99fafabff33603b17476b71ee26da8a","tid":1623309,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T19:47:43.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b27a3ce8b1f723ae3102ad1530787842d52f3f76","tid":16233